data.text:
Jane Russell and Bob Hope star in 'The Paleface' (1948), a classic Western comedy. In this film, Hope plays 'Painless' Peter Potter, a bumbling dentist who unwittingly becomes a hero in the Old West, while Russell portrays Calamity Jane, a sharp-shooting undercover agent.
